import org.apache.spark.sql._
val sqlContext = new SQLContext(sc)
val banks = sqlContext.read.format("com.databricks.spark.csv").option("header", "true").load("file:///shared/data/banks.csv")
banks.write.format("parquet").save("hdfs://namenode:8020/trade/ref/banks.parquet")

val ccps = sqlContext.read.format("com.databricks.spark.csv").option("header", "true").load("file:///shared/data/ccps.csv")
ccps.write.format("parquet").save("hdfs://namenode:8020/trade/ref/ccps.parquet")

val exchanges = sqlContext.read.format("com.databricks.spark.csv").option("header", "true").load("file:///shared/data/exchanges.csv")
exchanges.write.format("parquet").save("hdfs://namenode:8020/trade/ref/exchanges.parquet")

val symbols = sqlContext.read.format("com.databricks.spark.csv").option("header", "true").load("file:///shared/data/symbols_clean.csv")
symbols.write.format("parquet").save("hdfs://namenode:8020/trade/ref/symbols.parquet")
